.I val timed_write 
: 
.B Unix.file_descr -> bytes -> int -> int -> float -> int
.sp
Behave as 
.B ThreadUnix\&.read
and 
.B ThreadUnix\&.write
, except that
.B Unix_error(ETIMEDOUT,_,_)
is raised if no data is
available for reading or ready for writing after 
.B d
seconds\&.
The delay 
.B d
is given in the fifth argument, in seconds\&.

